description: "Map of maritime Southeast Asia, with four inset maps of locations in the region: Surabaya, some of the Lesser Sumba Islands, and Buton and Muna islands of the coast of Sulawesi. Mountains, forests, settlements and fields are represented pictorially."
title: "La nouvelle grande carte des Indes Orientales. Partie de la nouvelle grande carte des Indes Orientales : contenant les isles de Borneo, Iava, Celebes, Mindanao, Gilolo, Moluques, La Nouvelle Guinée, La Nouvelle Bretagne & les isles de Philippines avec les isles de Sumbawa, Serbira, Solor, Bouton & Pangesane."
